<section id="download" class="download">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="download-content">
      <h2>今すぐ脳活ラボを始めよう</h2>
      <p>無料ダウンロードで、健康維持と地域活性化の一歩を踏み出しましょう。</p>
      <div class="app-buttons">
        <a href="#" class="app-button">
          <img src="/assets/app-store-badge.svg" alt="App Storeからダウンロード" loading="lazy">
        </a>
        <a href="#" class="app-button">
          <img src="/assets/google-play-badge.svg" alt="Google Playからダウンロード" loading="lazy">
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .download {
    background-color: var(--color-indigo);
    color: white;
    padding: 4rem 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .download-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .download h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: white;
  }

  .download p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .app-buttons {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .app-button {
    display: inline-block;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .app-button:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
  }

  .app-button img {
    height: 50px;
    width: auto;
  }

  @media (min-width: 481px) {
    .app-buttons {
      flex-direction: row;
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 769px) {
    .download h2 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .download p {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .app-button img {
      height: 60px;
    }
  }
</style>
